---
title: Smart Asian-Style Chicken Thigh Salad  with Creamy Sriracha Dressing
description: Hearty chicken, juicy clementines, edamame and peanuts are the foundation for a tasty salad, that gets drizzled with a creamy and nutty sesame dressing.

